==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bongo
<hw>Bon"go</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Either of two large
antelopes (<spn>Bo⟦oum⟧cercus eurycercus</spn> of West Africa, and
<spn>Bo⟦oum⟧cercus isaaci</spn> of East Africa) of a reddish or
chestnut-brown color with narrow white stripes on the body. Their flesh
is especially esteemed as food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bongo</ent>⟦br⟧

