==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Bongo
<hw>Bon"go</hw> <pr>(b⟦ocr⟧⟦nsm⟧"g⟦omac⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>bongos</plw> or <plw>bongo</plw>.</plu> <def>one
